n innovative journey into emotional well-being powered by artificial intelligence. This app bridges technology and human emotions, enabling users to have natural and meaningful conversations with a generative AI therapist that responds with understanding and relevance.\n\nAI Therapist provides a non-judgmental space for individuals to explore their feelings, thoughts, and emotions. Whether seeking reflection, support, or new ways to connect with your inner self, AI Therapist delivers realistic interactions for a deeper understanding of emotions.\n\nKey Features:\n\n\u2022 Immersive 3D interface for engaging therapy sessions.\n\u2022 Realistic AI conversations for emotional support.\n\u2022 A safe platform for self-discovery and growth.\n\u2022 Perfect for daily check-ins, with an AI that offers effective assistance.\n\nNote: AI Therapist is experimental and not a substitute for professional therapy. It represents a step towards leveraging AI for emotional well-being, offering companionship on the path to self-improvement.", "short_description": "Explore emotions with AI: AI Therapist: Your Emotional Guide offers innovative therapy sessions with generative AI for emotional self-discovery. Experience natural conversations where the AI understands and guides you through your feelings, creating a unique space for emotional exploration."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://doc-hosting.flycricket.io/ai-therapist-your-emotional-guide-privacy-policy/2d3288f3-8fd3-4db4-9fdb-8ef6efb526a3/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Raetae Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://aitherapist.rf.gd/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "619566195371476"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUI